Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright and \Nsit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.66,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sanzenin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.65,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A party to celebrate my \Nacceptance into Hakuou Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Quite the brilliant \Nidea, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not official yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I feel like we're getting \Nahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have nothing to worry about! \NYou're bound to have been accepted!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually feeling a bit \Nconfident about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was disturbed in this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.72,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher administering the \Ntest played games with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, even the monkeys \Nhad their fun with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't... get to go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I put forth my \Nabsolute best effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.13,0:01:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, I was lucky that all \Nthe questions were multiple choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really good at that "pick \None out of three" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, that's the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.10,0:01:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.14,0:01:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the boxes, why \Ndid you open that one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me! Pardon me, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly seem good at \Nthree-choice questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:55.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, if Hayate had \Ndispassionately acknowledged
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how unlucky he is at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:01.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he may have avoided the comedy, \NI mean, tragedy in this episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but then again, maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:07.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:10.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is one who waits upon others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is a formal guardian,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:16.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who is there to support his mistress \Nin all aspects of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:22.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is about a boy who fights and puts \Nhis life on the line for a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A super combat battle story!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At minus 40 degrees Celsius, \Nyou can hammer nails with a banana!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I wanna eat perilla pickled eggplants.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:39.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi ni kaketa bokura no yukue
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:39.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination that we've \Nstaked upon this earth
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuki-nukeru hayate no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the sudden gale that cuts across
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Unmei ni makete
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:49.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving in to fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:54.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shagami-komu nante tsumannai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:54.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And hunkering down is no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:58.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore ja kakko warui yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:58.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uso kara deta makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:01.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Many a true word is spoken in jest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:07.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Koukai wa kitto mi kara deta sabi
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:07.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Regret is probably reaping what you sowed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zettai, nase ba naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:10.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Where there's a will, \Nthere's definitely a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:17.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ooki na hamon ni nomi-komareteku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:17.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As a great rippling wave swallows us up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:23.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Karada nami ni makasereba
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.74,0:03:23.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it take you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:26.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanchigai no yume
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:26.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreams that are misguided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mato-hazure no kitai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:30.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopes that are way off base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:35.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tsuyoku omoeba itsuka tsukameru sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:35.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll grab them someday, \Nif you just have conviction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:42.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Daichi keri-age hashiri-dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:42.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick up the earth and start running
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimama ni mau kaze no gotoku
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the capricious breeze that dances about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:05.46,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,285)}Hey, hey! I hafta go to a party.\N Hurry up, seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HINA!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hina! There's big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's turned into a huge mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you to knock before \Ncoming into my room, haven't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:29.85,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,25)}Don't make us show this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. Really, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Sis, knocking is \Nmankind's greatest invention!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat you for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuki dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you were home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you'd called.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you handling living \Non your own all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! Have faith in your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lavishing my \Nmoney on male companions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,nor have I fallen for me-me \Ncons or phishing e-mails!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But I wish you'd let me see the \Nplace you're living in just once...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having an important conversation \Nwith Hina right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you just bring up milk tea \Nand some kind of Japanese sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the double! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it sweet! Make the milk tea sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three sugars, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really do whatever you \Nfeel like, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! Bean jam pancakes really are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you'd get along with the \Ncat-type robot from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a happy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Didn't you come here to \Ntalk to me about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daf wighf! Dere's bif, \Nbif, bif, pwouble, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk or eat! Pick one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sanzenin butler actually came to \Ntake the transfer admission test!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for Hayate. \NHakuou's admission tests are hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as Nagi's butler, I'd assume \Nfailure wasn't an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine he must have put \Nsome serious effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get in his way, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uh-oh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a tiny prank! \NIt was meant to be a little joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined he would fall short \Nof passing by just one point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop breathing like that! \NYou're spreading the Dark Side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, going around \Nruining other people's lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, his not passing \Nis largely due to your prank
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the superintendent has ordered \Nyou to notify him of the results,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why you've \Ncome to me. Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you please, that is exactly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, about the only person \Nwe can discuss this with is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon? Not accepted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, so we'd like to deliver the \Nnews and apologize in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so vewy sowwie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know, \NI'm not coming with you for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is only proper that the Hakuou \NAcademy student body president
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.58,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should undertake this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's my little sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you apologize to Hayate \Nproperly and sincerely, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd suspected that something \Nlike this might happen, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this has me at a loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting and wear the \Noutfit that I tell you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the party's guest of honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with what I'm wearing now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! \NHurry up and get changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the outfit of your choice \Nis bound to be a sailor uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or something with animal ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.70,0:07:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wrong! I've got this for tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like with this atmosphere, \Nit's too late to be revealing the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what should I do? \NWhat should I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? What should I do? \NWhat should I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:07:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, g-good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here! It's Andromeda cake from Okadaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had trouble deciding between this \Nand the turtle bread from Pantasia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, why don't you at least come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so where's Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.03,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,45)}Congratulations to Miss Nagi's \NButler, Hayate Ayasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:41.03,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,120)}Hakuou Academy Acceptance Commemoration Party
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without an occasion such as this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Miss could never be persuaded \Nto host a social event, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she showed the slightest \Ninterest in doing so today,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we are holding a magnificent party \Nto make up for how rare these are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we owe it all to that boy \Ngaining acceptance into Hakuou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot tell you how \Ntroublesome he has been,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he has finally done something \Nof service to the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think you're going, Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something urgent came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.64,0:09:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me. He loves me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me. He loves me not. \NHe loves me. He loves me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loves me. He loves me not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, this is too much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the language of flowers, \Ncorn stands for trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and I are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're dancing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, it's almost embarrassing \Nhow merry they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have made him really \Nhappy that he passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is wholly the result of the \Nthorough instruction I gave the boy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regarding taking entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I also lit a fire under him, \Nthat he'd be fired if he didn't pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, my chronic peritonitis has caused \Nneuralgia, turning into a hordeolum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please don't mind me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear! Damn that Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I really wanted was a cosplay \Nparty with just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't a celebration for you, \NI'd have skipped out long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miss, you look quite \Nfabulous in that dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You outshine every last one \Nof the other guests here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You dummy! You're the star of the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes me happy to hear it.\N Thank you very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're happy, \NI suppose I'll let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation makes bringing up the \Nsubject even harder than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Given that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:04.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please enjoy this merriment \Nfor a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shish kebabs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan! It's Goh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.92,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,75)}Congratulations to Miss Nagi's \NButler, Hayate Ayasaki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.92,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,150)}Hakuou Academy Acceptance Commemoration Party
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to at least wait \Nuntil the party's over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't carry it out, \NI wouldn't be an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it isn't Miss Katsura. Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is... The truth is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has gone to the trouble of \Npersonally coming from Hakuou Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to celebrate the acceptance of Miss \NNagi's butler, Hayate Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go on! Give us a brief \Nspeech, if you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Ayasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are! An acceptance present!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really worked hard for this! \NIt makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.13,0:12:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:36.77,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a counter! \NThat, just now, was a counter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought an adult carries \Nout her responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because! It's just because!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, we have Miss Nagi's close \Nfriend, Miss Isumi Saginomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she will be delivering \Na congratulatory address.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Isumi became lost on her way over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she was apparently taken \Ninto safe custody earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at a souvenir shop on the shore of Lake Mashu, \Nso that will have to wait until another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same old Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she managed to \Nget off the main island...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Miss Nagi's cousin, Miss Sakuya \NAizawa has sent a congratulatory gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unveil it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title is "Soaring"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:30.15,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(315,280)}Soaring
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it is soaring?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the size or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this is a rare party \Nto celebrate your acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad that both Isumi \Nand Sakuya couldn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Katsura and Hinagiku are here. \NThat's more than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, why are \Nyou here, too, Hinagiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not accepted?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Keep your voice down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! Surely, of all people,\N Hayate couldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth, so there's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to let him know somehow, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we tell him that he didn't \Nget accepted after all this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, why did you guys \Ndecide that he'd been accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when you hadn't received any word?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you use your influence \Nas student body president?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to go there, what about \Nthe Sanzenin family's influence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, our festivities are \Nin full swing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is this "full swing" \Nfrom "festivities in full swing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be a kind of lassoing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, Hayate Ayasaki will now \Noffer a speech of thanks for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many of you have come to celebrate \Ntonight for little old me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that I might \Nget to go back to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really like a dream come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I'd given up on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I could never go back to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To laugh and fool around with \Nmy classmates at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those days were ordinary, and yet, \Nso dazzling and precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:10.69,On Top,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Culture Fest
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that no matter \Nhow much I wished it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those experiences would never \Nbe mine to have again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, Miss Nagi has made \Nthis wish of mine come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.29,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To have the pleasure of serving \Nsuch a kind mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the luckiest butler in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I have some very \Ndisappointing news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappointing news...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.79,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she... Will she finally tell him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be my \Nhomeroom teacher, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, certainly, with you \Nas my homeroom teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine I have a pretty tough \Nschool life ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I might get beaten down \Nboth physically and mentally,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm slightly apprehensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.81,0:16:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that will turn out \Nto be fun in its own way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan to \Nkeep fooling around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when I look into those innocent eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't bring myself to say it! \NOr rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, damn you! Get a clue already! \NOr rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm agonizing so much over here \Nand he's smiling like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! I'm suddenly feeling \Nthis surge of anger in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:48.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the truth about his \Nnon-acceptance to my grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That academy is fricking huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never notice one fake student!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.32,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that scares Yukiji Katsura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of nonsense are you spouting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsensers are gonna catch Hellers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what is this merry conversation about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too bad, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we went to visit Katsy's room, \Nwe found this on her desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(324,170)}Not Accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We figured Hayata would be \Nfeeling quite despondent,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we came to cheer him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really too bad, Hayata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.89,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, you must think there \Nis only darkness ahead of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that no good will come \Nof living out your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, mistakes made in your youth \Nwill prove valuable in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you get \Nstomped into the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rise up again like a weed, \Nlike Princess Sara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.30,0:17:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up, Hayata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shot of fight to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Hayata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I haven't quite grasped \Nthe situation yet, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:15.50,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(313,90)}Not Accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the upshot of it was that I \Nwas not accepted... Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So roast me or boil me, do \Nwhatever you want with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, just kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.56,0:18:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay out here for too long, \Nyou're going to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and Miss Katsura and the \Nothers are worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have done a terrible \Ndisservice to the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to Miss Katsura and Hinagiku, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all the people who \Ncelebrated with me today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault for getting really \Nhappy and getting my hopes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stupid, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I came to this great mansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't have \Nany hopes for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that way, \NI wouldn't have to suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd learned that lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as I allowed myself to be spoiled
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.18,0:19:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by the Miss's kindness and \Nyours and everyone else's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I had begun to forget that \Nmost basic of lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.54,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to be empty, because \Nyou have nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think such an empty person \Nis qualified to be Nagi's butler?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course, I'm aware that \NI've been a burden in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I plan to pull myself \Ntogether more than ever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and do my best from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.27,0:20:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? But the look on your face says you can't \Npossibly do your best all on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.94,0:20:37.41,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,120)}Student ID
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go here and study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is from Hakuou Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My student ID?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I submitted a recommendation for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with that added, \NI had them deem that you passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because an empty person \Nwho has nothing to lose
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,does not have the qualifications \Nto be her butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.26,0:20:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, I think there will come a day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.50,0:21:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you will truly be required to \Nuse your abilities to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please become Nagi's first-rate butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Hakuou and I'll become \Na first-rate butler, without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a first-rate butler, \Nfor Maria's sake, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.63,0:21:35.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It isn't for my sake, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:37.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:41.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe how boldly \NI behaved towards Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:45.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that was the story of how Maria \Nbecame embarrassed way too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:48.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're going to get embarrassed, \Ndon't do it in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:51.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, he'll fight the \Nexpectations of high school girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:22:00.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Naida kokoro no ho ni kaze ga fuki-nuketetta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:22:00.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze crossed the wilted sail of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:05.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kimochi yureru soshite Lose My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:05.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings waver and then I lose my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zutto kimi ga iru nara ii ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:08.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if you'll always be here, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:12.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sore mo waruku wa nai So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:12.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tenki-yohou nante nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather forecasts don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Zenbu kibun-shidai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:18.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all mood-dependent
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:21.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nanimo shinpai nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:21.45,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Makasete! Jiyuu-jizai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:24.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! Perfectly free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Keri-ageta kutsu ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,On the shoe that I kick up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:29.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Put A Wish" Zettai hareru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:29.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Put a Wish" it'll definitely clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:31.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kekka wa... I'm Looking At Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:31.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And the result is, I'm looking at nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:34.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mou ichido, yari-naoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:34.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, a do-over!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama ni wa kakete-miyou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try betting once in a while
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:42.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nee kimi ni yudanete-mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:42.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I want to try entrusting you with it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:47.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sassou to kake-nukete To Fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:47.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Running through gallantly, to fly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Harema ga mieru The Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:49.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see a break in the weather, the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:51.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shinjiteta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:51.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:54.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soshite Make My Way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:54.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I make my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:57.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sotto sashi-dasu kimi no te de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.72,0:22:57.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With the hand you quietly reach out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:02.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Muteki ni nareru kara So I Go Together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:23:02.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become invincible, so I go together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:10.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hoshi ga kirei da ashita mo hareru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.96,0:23:10.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stars so beautiful, it'll \Nbe clear again tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:29.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,...Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:30.38,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(322,240)}Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morn-even-noon! I'm Nagi Sanzenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.78,0:23:33.93,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:35.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll be able to go to \Nschool, after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.95,0:23:39.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:43.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to study hard in order to \Nacquit myself well as your butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:44.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:47.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're seriously thinking \Nabout your future with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.23,0:23:51.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:54.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just meditating a little. \NIt's Aura Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:55.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:59.15,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,240)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:59.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I was in high spirits, \Njust by getting accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:02.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,but I transferred with borderline grades. \NWill I really be able to cut it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.15,0:24:19.17,OS,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of "Hayate \Nthe Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.36,0:24:07.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, you must always be \Nreading two or three moves ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.69,0:24:10.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Waking up early can certainly pay off. \NYou get to meet interesting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:13.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make the jab that he's the most \Ninteresting person here, would I lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:14.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.73,0:24:16.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.10,0:24:18.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Samurai, the Way of the \NWarrior, Van Damme in Action".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.37,0:24:19.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Himuro, is that enough with the flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:22.17,Default,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai, the Way of the Warrior, \NVan Damme in Action
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.87,0:24:21.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Little Master Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:24.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The things Ayasaki does are dangerous, \Nso never try them at home.
